{"tid":333786,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[HX UO mola mola]中國部分銀行傳暫停對海航發放新貸款","createTime":"2017-07-24T07:00:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-24T16:16:14.000Z","uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b83040cd3f51998806faf402cc7355735f88f8e5","tid":333786,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T07:00:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/china/article/1614652/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E9%8A%80%E8%A1%8C%E5%82%B3%E6%9A%AB%E5%81%9C%E5%B0%8D%E6%B5%B7%E8%88%AA%E7%99%BC%E6%94%BE%E6%96%B0%E8%B2%B8%E6%AC%BE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fchina%2Farticle%2F1614652%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%2583%25A8%25E5%2588%2586%25E9%258A%2580%25E8%25A1%258C%25E5%2582%25B3%25E6%259A%25AB%25E5%2581%259C%25E5%25B0%258D%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E8%2588%25AA%25E7%2599%25BC%25E6%2594%25BE%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%25B2%25B8%25E6%25AC%25BE&d=nx8jq1ClmvvomQoMDLd9JZnkJiu3DM%2BvEze6mtExKRo%3D&h=70582955\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/china/article/1614652/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E9%8A%80%E8%A1%8C%E5%82%B3%E6%9A%AB%E5%81%9C%E5%B0%8D%E6%B5%B7%E8%88%AA%E7%99%BC%E6%94%BE%E6%96%B0%E8%B2%B8%E6%AC%BE</a><br />\n<br />\n外電引述知情人士透露，中國部分銀行已決定暫停對海航發放新貸款。<br />\n<br />\n知情人士稱，有三家銀行已決定暫停對海航發放新貸款，其中一家於今年年初暫停，另外一家於兩個月前；第三家銀行則是新近採取上述舉措。而第四家銀行過去幾個月減少對海航的風險敞口，並降低一項授信。<br />\n<br />\n截至2015年對海航授信額度最大的八家銀行中，上述四家銀行均名列其中。<br />\n<br />\n海航表示，該公司財務狀況依然強勁，公司資產負債率於2016財年連續第7年下降，公司並不依賴於單一的的融資渠道。<br />\n<br />\n海航上周表示，因市場原因，美銀退出與海航集團旗下一家成員企業的相關業務。<br />\n<br />\n《華爾街日報》早前引述知情人士稱，中國政府近期對大型民營企業海外投資的限制，得到中國國家主席習近平的批准。受限制的包括大連萬達集團、海航集團、安邦保險集團和復星國際。"},{"pid":"43851c106cb0f0fccdf2f087a07b6c4da827c4b4","tid":333786,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T07:07:37.000Z","msg":"班大種乞衣會唔會重繼續買快運， 唔驚執？"},{"pid":"0d7613cb235697b76d4c9757cc8ac032bd612adf","tid":333786,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T07:08:08.000Z","msg":"等睇Fuck星呢間最叻認屎認屁既企業收皮"},{"pid":"0c835cc3be95b407b3eb65e1f4a20685c68ead71","tid":333786,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T07:09:30.000Z","msg":"印錢就得啦，點會唔肯借，有人失勢?"},{"pid":"f1050957c94b06faa57702000d4ae403f9808479","tid":333786,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T07:12:03.000Z","msg":"又多間"},{"pid":"898c599cad917db438c8c1eaa7284b361814f4cd","tid":333786,"uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T07:13:52.000Z","msg":"王生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2d7837882fde6a87a74408e38a1213abe43ff9f","tid":333786,"uid":117556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T07:28:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>王生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n郭文貴D料好堅？"},{"pid":"e967e49583c6745679947de9dd1ee3c8053fa753","tid":333786,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T16:16:14.000Z","msg":"罷坐HX/UO<br />\n送佢一程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}